com.joliciel.talismane.sentenceAnnotators

Class RegexTokenAnnotator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.joliciel.talismane.sentenceAnnotators.AbstractRegexAnnotator
      • com.joliciel.talismane.sentenceAnnotators.RegexTokenAnnotator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Annotator<Sentence>, RegexAnnotator, SentenceAnnotator

    public class RegexTokenAnnotator
extends AbstractRegexAnnotator
    A regex annotator which tokenises the matched group as a single separate token, and offers the possibility of a replacement string to replace the token text.

    In addition to the parameters recognised by AbstractRegexAnnotator, recognises:
    • replacement: see getReplacement().
    • analysisText: see getAnalysisText().

    Author:
    Assaf Urieli
